#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn54.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Ekadhammavagga "
msgstr "1. One Thing "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Ariṭṭhasutta "
msgstr "6. With Ariṭṭha "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.315, sc1
msgctxt "sn54.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.6:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā … pe … etadavoca: "
msgstr "There the Buddha … said: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.6:1.3"
msgid "“bhāvetha no tumhe bhikkhave, ānāpānassatin”ti? "
msgstr "“Mendicants, do you develop mindfulness of breathing?” "

msgctxt "sn54.6:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ariṭṭho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, Venerable Ariṭṭha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.6:1.5"
msgid "“ahaṃ kho, bhante, bhāvemi ānāpānassatin”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, I develop mindfulness of breathing.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.6:1.6"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, ariṭṭha, bhāvesi ānāpānassatin”ti? "
msgstr "“But mendicant, how do you develop it?” "

# NOTE: Compare a similar construction at SN 21.10.
#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: ajjhattabahiddhā → ajjhattaṃ bahiddhā (s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn54.6:1.7"
msgid "“Atītesu me, bhante, kāmesu kāmacchando pahīno, anāgatesu me kāmesu kāmacchando vigato, ajjhattabahiddhā ca me dhammesu paṭighasaññā suppaṭivinītā. "
msgstr "“Sir, I’ve given up desire for sensual pleasures of the past. I’m rid of desire for sensual pleasures of the future. And I have eliminated perception of repulsion regarding phenomena internally and externally. "

# NOTE: BB follows sinala reading which gives the verb in present tense. I take the future tense as future evidence of his partial understanding of the practice.
#. VAR: So → sohaṃ (?)
msgctxt "sn54.6:1.8"
msgid "So satova assasissāmi, satova passasissāmi. "
msgstr "Just mindful, I will breathe in. Mindful, I will breathe out. "

msgctxt "sn54.6:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhāvemi ānāpānassatin”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how I develop mindfulness of breathing.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn54.6:2.1"
msgid "“‘Atthesā, ariṭṭha, ānāpānassati, nesā natthī’ti vadāmi. "
msgstr "“That is mindfulness of breathing, Ariṭṭha; I don’t deny it. "

msgctxt "sn54.6:2.2"
msgid "Api ca, ariṭṭha, yathā ānāpānassati vitthārena paripuṇṇā hoti "
msgstr "But as to how mindfulness of breathing is fulfilled in detail, "

msgctxt "sn54.6:2.3"
msgid "taṃ suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi; bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.6:2.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā ariṭṭho bhagavato paccassosi. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” Ariṭṭha replied. "

msgctxt "sn54.6:2.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn54.6:3.1"
msgid "“Kathañca, ariṭṭha, ānāpānassati vitthārena paripuṇṇā hoti? "
msgstr "“And how is mindfulness of breathing fulfilled in detail? "

msgctxt "sn54.6:3.2"
msgid "Idha, ariṭṭha, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or to an empty hut. They sit down cross-legged, with their body straight, and establish mindfulness right there. "

msgctxt "sn54.6:3.3"
msgid "So satova assasati, satova passasati. "
msgstr "Just mindful, they breathe in. Mindful, they breathe out. "

msgctxt "sn54.6:3.4"
msgid "Dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti … pe … "
msgstr "When breathing in heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing in heavily.’ When breathing out heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing out heavily.’ … "

msgctxt "sn54.6:3.5"
msgid "‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati. "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.6:3.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, ariṭṭha, ānāpānassati vitthārena paripuṇṇā hotī”ti. "
msgstr "This is how mindfulness of breathing is fulfilled in detail.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.6:3.7"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

